      <item>
        <title>Happy 70th Evert Jan Baerends!</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;All the best for your &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.acmm.nl/activities/index.php&quot;&gt;70th birthday Evert Jan Baerends!&lt;/a&gt; Already during my undergraduate studies I was impressed by your outstanding contributions related to DFT and still today I end up with your publications whenever I want to understand a problem in depth. It was a pleasure to join your group in Amsterdam for my PhD studies. Thank you very much for the pleasant scientific environment with many inspiring discussions.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

